ZH: 我是一名志愿者，经常参加社区活动。
EN: I am a volunteer and regularly participate in community events.

ZH: 明天我要去一个志愿者培训会。
EN: Tomorrow, I will be attending a volunteer training session.

ZH: 我非常喜欢为他人服务，所以成为一名志愿者是理想的选择。
EN: I enjoy serving others, so becoming a volunteer is an ideal choice for me.

ZH: 这个组织招募了许多年轻志愿者。
EN: This organization has recruited many young volunteers.

ZH: 许多志愿者为了公益事业放弃了自己的时间和利益。
EN: Many volunteers sacrifice their time and personal interests for the sake of public welfare.

ZH: 志愿者的贡献对社会有着重要的影响。
EN: The contributions of volunteers have a significant impact on society.

ZH: 志愿者们每周都会定期清理公园。
EN: Volunteers clean the park regularly every week.

ZH: 我们的志愿者团队需要更多人加入。
EN: Our volunteer team needs more people to join.

ZH: 她在医院做志愿者工作，帮助病人。
EN: She works as a volunteer in the hospital, assisting patients.

ZH: 明天我们将会举办一场志愿者座谈会。
EN: We will be holding a volunteer symposium tomorrow.

ZH: 他通过志愿者工作来锻炼自己的领导能力。
EN: He develops his leadership skills through volunteer work.

ZH: 志愿者们在敬老院里陪伴老人度过愉快的时光。
EN: Volunteers spend quality time with the elderly in the nursing home.

ZH: 志愿者们每天为流浪动物提供食物和水。
EN: Volunteers provide food and water for stray animals daily.

ZH: 这个项目需要许多热心的志愿者来支持。
EN: This project requires many dedicated volunteers for support.

